lead_paragraph: Matt Besler scored in stoppage time to help Sporting Kansas City beat the Columbus Crew 3-2 on Sunday night and extend its unbeaten streak to four games.

headline.print_headline: Besler Scores in Stoppage Time, Sporting KC Beats Crew 3-2
